name: Lunarbits
description: Lunarbits, a Bitcoin token built on the Runes protocol, is a community project of space, art, music, and Bitcoin lovers. The community celebrates the historic event when Lunarbits QR Code-embedded digital artifacts launched atop the SpaceX Falcon 9 in a private payload (Lunaprise Payload on IM-1 Mission) and landed in a time capsule on the moon on February 22, 2024. The popular space, art, and music community is famous for celebrating alongside the Bitcoin industry, music festivals, art fairs, digital collectible meetups, and space-themed events.
